 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "5602061f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Logical Operators\n",
    "Logical operators are used to combine conditional statements:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. and\n",
    "2. or\n",
    "3. not"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "06a23651",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 1. and"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "1dad65d7",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "True\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "x=5;\n",
    "print(x>0 and x<10);"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f404093f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2. or"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "a0047907",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "False\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "x = 5\n",
    "\n",
    "print(x < 5 or x > 10)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "0bf27bd3",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 3. not"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "346a77c0",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "False\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "x = 5\n",
    "\n",
    "print(not(x > 3 and x < 10))"
   ]
  }
 ],
